title: Statistics on Obesity, Physical Activity and Diet 2020: Data tables
description: Contains tabulated outputs for obesity related hospital admissions and prescriptions for the treatment of obesity.
datasetNotes: On landing page scroll down to heading "Data Sets" for link to latest release.
sizingNotes: Large number of tabs, some tabs simple but some messy structure of tables. Multiple dimension & sub-dimensions. Quite a few footnotes.
